<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />For he established covenant decrees in Jacob</para>

<para style="q1">and appointed a law in Israel.</para>

<para style="q1">He commanded our ancestors</para>

<para style="q1">that they were to teach them to their children.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />He commanded this so that the generation to come might know his decrees, the children not yet born,</para>

<para style="q1">who should tell them in turn to their own children.</para>
